Marrakech,Zpj1ruy5pp8,Ugxw67GBvUPvei-HGi54AaABAg,,@artdirector9517,"Nice vlog 👌Yeah Kingdom of Morocco is stuning as package, his landscapes is incredibley diverse. Sahara desert, oasis, woods, snow, rivers, two water fronts long ocean coastline and mediterranean golden sand. surf spot, mountains, old medinas, vibrant souks, festivals, colorful cities etc.. He has too a rich culture of food, music, hand craft, traditionnel clothing, home furnitur, interior design, tiles etc.. As you can see in Marrakech city as berber saharien or in Tanger as mauresque with some spanish archetecture touch, the city that contains the world's first United States embassy in the history. Also kingdom of Morocco is the first country to recognize USA in the world at 1777. We are so open as civilisation for exemple about the spanish influences, they were in the north of Morocco for almost 50 yeras but not problem becaus we were in their country for 800 years 😊 that's pretty much isn't ?! lool. We left the last city Grenada at january of 1492, Just a few month later, they discovered America at october of 92 by Columbus using our tools. they translated too our books left in the university of Cordoba the best university in the world at that time. Two years after Spain become the new bigest super power on earth with Portugal. Why not ?! nothing was missing 🙂. Just for information it's the empire of Morocco who built almost 60 % of spanish cities. for exemple Garnata city become Grenada, Ichbillia city become Sevilla, kortoba become Cordoba, Balancia become Valencia etc.. It's so easy isn't ! 😎 as it is for the 40 other cities. All this legacy of sciences has crossed borders of the Andalousie reached France then to England and Florence city in Italy by Sicily island to declare the edge of renaissance in europe. For information, the oldest university in the world called Al-Qarawiyyin in Fez city and while there were 400 Hamam (bath) in Sevilla city and oil-powered lamp-posts in her streets there were any one in Paris or London. also is the oldest kingdom systeme in the world too with japan .Any way we are brothers every one of us carries the torch of progress. For reference, Steve Jobs' father is Syrian but the most signifiant of all this is the first traveler in the history and the first who draw a map of the planet earth were too moroccans, They are Ibn Battuta and Al-Idrissi. So strange isn't ?! 🤔 especialy it was a right map even without satellite 😅. Any way last time Morocco become the hidden paradise of surfers, motobikers, caravaners, stylists, artist, photographers, and digital nomades 🤫 in short when god reduces the world in half millions klm he gives Mor-occo. Joy it as you can, life is too short than you think. Hey 🙂 nice video 👍 keep going 🙏 .'''.'.''.''.'.'",2025-03-13T15:23:32Z,2025-03-13T15:23:32Z,2,False,0.0,2026-04-27T02:01:57.797746
Marrakech,Zpj1ruy5pp8,Ugxfdocs1PHGrdxmiYF4AaABAg,,@artdirector9517,"this country is safe you have just to : 1 - put your back-bag on your chest in the crowded souks. 2 - bargain is part of the culture so you can bargaining about every price, it's normal in souks, propos always the half price pretends to leave and wait for his reaction. 3 - if you get lost just ask kiosk owners or old age locals or their ki dss is better 😉 4 - it's so easy to rent a car, renting a car doesn't cost too much like 30 dollars. 5 - taxis is very sheap too from 1 dollar just ask the taxi driver to turn on the distance metter it's obligatory for him. 6 - if you look for an tasty first Tagine experience. the real Tagine is : is when cooked directly in Tagine pot in live, is when meat is sticky on honeyed form but better if it was cooked on coal. Some streets activities prices : Henee hand tatoe cost like 8 dollars. Tips for musicians like 2 dollars but if you film with them a dance, more. Tips for Sneaks charmer like 2 dollars but if you shoot a vlog video with them, more. Short Camel ride or pigmy horse ride from 5 dollars. the golden advice here is : fixed the price with each one of them before to make easier your travel. Just free you mind and joy it as you can. A great kingdom, beautiful country and a welcoming people good luck 👍 my purpose is avoiding problems and misunderstandings between tourists and locals because I feel sad when I see a vlog that deals with small incidents that don't even deserve to be anxious about them, especially when traveling. Tips (few money) is nothing compared to a moment of joy. life is too short to live it with anxiety. Peace and love 🙏 nice vlog 👍 keep going. '.'.'.'.''.''.'.'",2025-03-13T15:21:43Z,2025-03-14T04:50:16Z,6,False,3.0,2026-04-27T02:01:57.797750
