Tourism,cRdwAQD1OKE,UgwRev3_OaXaLS_wncd4AaABAg,,@skibum4cy,"Lived & worked in international education in Cebu for over three years...tourists & longer-term residence are choosing other destinations. The unreliable basics, poor infrastructure, traffic, trash, poverty, corruption, etc. all make it less & less appealing for visitors & foreign residents each & every month. What was once the Pearl of the Orient & had every single advantage imaginable coming out of WWII has been squandered & is now so far behind SE Asian peers that it's hard to see them ever get back what they once had. A shame, but the reality is glaring.",2026-04-26T14:58:41Z,2026-04-26T14:58:41Z,0,False,0.0,2026-04-27T02:02:28.221069
