Tourism,cRdwAQD1OKE,Ugwvn1NbKHqJajQNWVh4AaABAg,,@LAPOINTE3THOMAS,"Betrayal? Yes im beginning to feel that. Im a merchant mariner; half fhillpno white guy born in ph. Been working in the states and living in ph since pandemic. My dream and love is dying being in ph... i live there 6months out of year. Everything you say about ph is true. Better in so many  places in asia; but only reason why i continue to return is partially my duel citizenship and i am almost forcing myself to live there. Ignoring all the bad things. I feel it is kinda a Betrayal knowing i will eventually leave for thailand, s. Korea or basically anywhere else in asia where ive been.  I want to love the ph; but i would only be flying 😔",2026-04-26T06:14:42Z,2026-04-26T06:14:42Z,0,False,1.0,2026-04-27T02:02:28.221095
