Tourism,cRdwAQD1OKE,UgxPta4jBizj5OIPoMp4AaABAg,,@edwardkearle7196,"Spend your money wisely, if u only want to go to the touristy places and resorts, why would u even go to the Phills? u can do that at home.  Try the provinces, much cheaper and more of a challenge finding your way around.. That's where most of the sites are anyhow.             Someone i knew here a while back took a holiday to Phills,  went straight from the airport to a plush resort, stayed there for a week then back to the airport and home again.. wth!!??  didn't see any of the Philippines, just the inside of a resort and the small piece of beach inside the resort boundary... may as well have stayed in a resort in the closest city to home...",2026-04-26T01:18:40Z,2026-04-26T01:18:40Z,3,False,0.0,2026-04-27T02:02:28.221116
