Tourism,cRdwAQD1OKE,UgyZYn6QP5jA9Thya8J4AaABAg,,@ArchiveForgotten,"I am living in the Philippines now and yes it's difficult to get here and glade I left before the oil went through the roof. I love it here even with the high prices. The people are warm and welcoming. Yes it's a poor country but than so are many parts of North America and it's getting worse by the day too. So the real question is, do you want to live in North America where it's getting worse by the day or leave for the warm tropical conditions of the Philippines or somewhere else in the world. At least they don't toss codes at you like they do in North America if your in the provinces.",2026-04-25T04:10:27Z,2026-04-25T04:10:27Z,2,False,0.0,2026-04-27T02:02:28.221153
