Tourism,cRdwAQD1OKE,UgxeBG7FrNdh9OIJWgh4AaABAg,,@markdavis6835,"I'm a US Navy Veteran living on Mindanao since 2019. I have been all over the world and there are places in SE Asia that have much better infrastructure, food and easier travel options. For me I don't think I can live anywhere else because I care about this place. For me there is no where more safe, I have an excellent VA in Manila, staying here long-term is easy and not expensive, the people are the kindest in the world and I have a life here. I from Las Vegas and left behind my grown son & my house because living here is the right choice. I'm getting ready to go back there for some needed surgery and the ticket is expensive, but you have to take the good with the bad. Lastly, I seriously doubt somebody like me who has been wounded in war and have quite a few negatives would ever find someone like I have anywhere else.  I is sad tourism has taken a hit, but for me I can do without ever seeing another foreigner ever again.",2026-04-23T05:13:22Z,2026-04-23T05:13:22Z,0,False,0.0,2026-04-27T02:02:28.221355
