Tourisme,5dJJ2gfMPiY,Ugxdyn9L7n1UJUsA76l4AaABAg,,@bystandersarah,"I’m sad that tourists ruin it for the local people but also for those of us who do respect, appreciate and genuinely want to learn when we visit. I would love to stay with people in their home, learn to make food, see things only locals know like secret tunnels, artists making things behind the scenes, gardens.  I haven’t gone because my friend in Mexico City is having a hard time with depression and my other friend from Guadalajara has a feud in her family. So, I guess I won’t visit for a while.😢I lost touch with another friend because he’s traveling rough right now, but eventually I would love to do a tour to visit all these Mexican friends. Hopefully México will treat me kindly.🙏🏼 I will treat México with awareness and love. Unless I fall in love with someone, I probably wouldn’t out stay my welcome😅",2026-03-21T20:25:53Z,2026-03-21T20:26:46Z,0,False,0.0,2026-04-27T02:03:54.750489
